Wiam Dahmani (Arabic) (a mụrụ na 22 Ọgọst 1983, Rabat, Morocco; nwụrụ: 22 Eprel 2018, Abu Dhabi, UAE) bụ onye Morocco na-eme ihe ngosi, onye na-emeeme ihe  na onye na-agụ egwu bi na UAE. O meela ihe nkiri Pakistani ole na ole dịka Ishq Khuda, Hijrat, na Hotal.
A mụrụ ya n'abalị 22, ọnwa August afọ 1983 na Rabat, Morocco
Ọ gụsịrị akwụkwọ na Mahadum America nke Sharjah na UAE ma nwee nzere Bachelor of Science na Sayensị gburugburu ebe obibi.
O buru ụzọ rụọ ọrụ dịka onye mgbasa ozi na ụlọ ọrụ telivishọn Dubai TV, wee gaa n'ọhịa nke ịbụ abụ ma mee vidiyo. N'afọ 2010, ọ malitekwara ịrụ ọrụ na India

N'afọ 2012, ọ gara n'ógbè nnọchiteanya ma mgbe nke ahụ gasịrị, ọ sonyere na usoro (Girls) onye na-eme ihe nkiri. O mere ihe nkiri Pakistani mbụ ya na Ishq Khuda, nke e wepụtara n'afọ 2013 ma bụrụ Average Grosser na Box Office. N'afọ 2016, ọ pụtara na ihe nkiri Pakistani abụọ Hijrat na Hotal, nke a kpọrọ "Item Girl"
Ọ rụkwara ọrụ dịka onye ngosi na Zee Aflam

Ọ nwụrụ n'ihi nkụchi obi n'abalị 22, ọnwa Eprel, afọ 2018. Ọ dị afọ 34 n'oge ọ nwụrụ. Dịka mgbasa ozi si kwuo, nne ya hụrụ ya nwụrụ anwụ n'ime ụlọ nkwari akụ ya na Abu Dhabi, ma lie ya n'oge na-adịbeghị anya n'otu obodo ahụ.
